      "content": "i'm just really scared to go to the hospital, it's so expensive and i hate the ER. if it was actually a stroke wouldn't it be more like... i don't know, paralysis or something? this just feels like a massive migraine flare up. can you just tell me what the difference is so i can be sure? i'd really rather just take a couple of my pills and rest if there's a chance it's just the migraine.",
